Page_0:
"Hey Tubbs!
Another wine bottle was stolen from the cellar last night. Wesley was found unconscious down there. He said that somebody had hit him on the head with a pan or something, but he hadn't been able to see the person. I wonder why Captain Bucksley keeps defending that drunkard Benny. The whole staff knows that he's got a drinking problem and that he lost his former job because of it. True, we haven't caught Benny being drunk on duty yet, but I bet he's keeping those bottles in his locker - that's why he snarls at everybody who just looks at it. Maybe you could check what's in the locker when Benny's not there.
                                    Todd"